      "url": "https://floss.social/@pottekkat/113504290534562277",
      "created_at": "2024-11-18T13:53:46.954Z",
      "content": "<p>I added a &quot;Today I Learned&quot; section to my blog to share the small stuff I learn every day.</p><p>My goal was to create a space where I can quickly publish shards of knowledge that would otherwise be lost to my future self and others.</p><p>I documented how I created this section for my Hugo blog here: <a href=\"https://navendu.me/posts/til-section-hugo/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" translate=\"no\"><span class=\"invisible\">https://</span><span class=\"ellipsis\">navendu.me/posts/til-section-h</span><span class=\"invisible\">ugo/</span></a></p>",
