    {
      "id": "113435897135736052",
      "url": "https://floss.social/@pottekkat/113435897135736052",
      "created_at": "2024-11-06T12:00:26.509Z",
      "content": "<p>I might be five years late in reading this, but Dries Buytaert clearly and concisely explains how we can build and sustain open source projects using easy-to-understand economic models.</p><p>This is a must-read for everyone thinking about building sustainable open source projects.</p><p>From &quot;Balancing Makers and Takers to scale and sustain Open Source.&quot;</p>",
